How to Setup the app:

Prerequisits for installation ruby 1.9.2p-180 using rvm or compiled.
In case you are installing ruby afresh, please make sure you install development headers for
libreadline and libzlib

gem install bundler
gem install rails -v="3.0.9"

bundle install 
rake db:create
rake db:migrate
rake db:seed

rails s

Known Issues to be cleared within this week :

Issues in Uploading Image using paperclip. Uses Gravatar http://en.gravatar.com/ at the moment.
